<p>John and Dave are in Las Vegas for BlogWorld Expo 2009 and deliver this week&#39;s show together from the hotel. Being on the road doesn&#39;t stop them, though, and the show goes through all your questions, troubles, tips and more. Plus, John shares his tale of woe&#8230; and the resolution he found! Subscribe today and don&#39;t miss another episode. It&#39;s free!</p>
